    "description": "For a pocket-sized portion that's full of flavour, try tossing juicy tomatoes, roasted green beans and chicken in a zingy pesto dressing. Top with crunchy walnuts and dig in. Smaller portion providing 2 of your 5-a-day and high in protein.",
